'''Coldtime''' was a season on [[Gamorr/Legends|Gamorr]] that was the equivalent of [[Winter/Legends|winter]]. It was a harsh period of freezing temperatures and blowing winds. Most [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorreans]] remained indoors at all times, forcing the warlike [[Gender/Legends|males]] to soften a bit, and resulting in much courtship and romance between the [[Gender/Legends|sexes]].<ref name="Slushtime">{{JournalCite|14|Murder in Slushtime}}</ref>

